{"tid":2162780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"受傷警員作供: 被告一拳令口腔內一粒痱滋爆裂 出現疼痛","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T06:41:55.000Z","uid":289214,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf1eef3cd79baa6968c3538ece8b13386d595f4","tid":2162780,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:48:57.000Z","msg":"去年6月26日，有大批示威者在灣仔警署總部外聚集，其間有便衣警員疑遭追打。事後一名25歲地盤工人，被控暴動和襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。案件今早在區域法院進行第二日審訊，控方傳召當日報稱受襲的警員張金福出庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n張金福在庭上指，他於案發當晚原定休假，收到上司電話後嘗試前往警總。混亂間懷疑遭人拳打兩下和腳踢一下。張金福報稱其中一拳擊中他右邊嘴角，令其口腔內的一粒痱滋爆裂，出現疼痛。<br />\n<br />\n警員張金福在庭上接受辯方盤問時說，事後並沒有求醫，只說痱滋痛了一個星期。辯方就指張金福在警方口供中，未有提及那粒痱滋因右臉被打而變得嚴重，質疑「傷勢」是否因而造成。<br />\n<br />\n聆訊明早繼續，張金福將繼續出庭作證。<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong>好痛</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/117445511_1237904859886254_1942089494300602074_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=tO6K2YWV7yMAX_QA91y&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg2-1.fna&amp;oh=723f31fad2f1ba9556d9a6d670719c88&amp;oe=5F62E1C4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F117445511_1237904859886254_1942089494300602074_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DtO6K2YWV7yMAX_QA91y%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg2-1.fna%26oh%3D723f31fad2f1ba9556d9a6d670719c88%26oe%3D5F62E1C4&h=95247ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1237904856552921/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fphotos%2Fa.384058221937593%2F1237904856552921%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=53cd6861\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1237904856552921/</a>"},{"pid":"49c5db3eecfc18bcbea436e2498d6087a0a2dee1","tid":2162780,"uid":268410,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20